# 🎨 DESIGN DOCUMENT — Portfolio Based on Example Layout

---

## 1️⃣ Overview

This document outlines how your portfolio will look and be structured, *in simple design terms*, just like the example:

📌 Clean typography
📌 Minimal spacing
📌 Full-page width sections
📌 Sections stacked vertically

---

## 2️⃣ Color & Style Guidelines

### 🎨 Color Palette

* **Primary Background:** Dark shade (#111827)
* **Text Color:** Soft white (#F8FAFC)
* **Accent Color:** Cyan (#0EA5E9)

### ✏️ Typography

* **Headings:** Bold, large (like 60–72px)
* **Body Text:** Medium, easy to read (16–20px)
* **Font Family:** Inter, Poppins, or Sans-Serif

### 📐 Spacing

* Large section padding: 80px top and bottom
* Consistent spacing between sections

---

## 3️⃣ Layout & Sections

The design is a **single-page portfolio** with smooth scrolling.

---

### 🧍‍♂️ 3.1 Hero Section

**Purpose:** Quick intro and first impression.

**Structure:**

```
┌───────────────────────────────────────┐
| Left Side: Text                        |
|   - Name (Large)                      |
|   - Title (e.g., Full Stack Developer)|
|   - Short Line (About you skill)      |
|   - Buttons: View Projects | Contact  |
|                                       |
| Right Side: Hero Image                |
└───────────────────────────────────────┘
```

**Styling:**

* Big bold name
* Strong accent button

---

### 💡 3.2 About Section

**Structure:**

```
About Me
[Profile photo — round]
A short paragraph about you
List of skills (icons + name)
```

**Skills can be shown like:**

```
JavaScript  | React | Node.js
CSS/HTML    | MongoDB | Git
```

---

### 💻 3.3 Projects Section

Each project card should have:

```
┌───────────────────────────────────┐
| PROJECT IMAGE                      |
| Project Title                     |
| Short Description                 |
| Tech stack (tags)                |
| Button: View Code / Live Demo    |
└───────────────────────────────────┘
```

Spacing similar to example: three columns in a row (responsive).

---

### 📚 3.4 Experience / Work Section

```
Experience
Job Title | Company
Date Range
Short description + achievements
```

Example:

```
CloudFactory - Image Annotation
May 2025 - Present
• Worked on annotating videos
• Built tagging system
```

---

### 📝 3.5 Contact / Call to Action

Should ask:

```
Let’s build something together
Email | LinkedIn | GitHub
```

Simple contact form or email link.

---

